Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:07.22,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724.091,814.091)\fade(255,0,255,0,2525,4940,6020)}Sūn Cè's Founding
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:11.99,Thinking,,0,0,0,,When Cáo Cāo and Lǚ Bù fought\Neach other at the borders of Shāndōng,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:15.88,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sūn Cè, reduced to a lower rank, was quietly building up his power in Jiāngdōng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:20.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,After his father Sūn Jiān had died,\NSūn Cè started planning his grand undertaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:24.00,Thinking,,0,0,0,,First, he escorted his mother and \Nother family members to Qū'ē,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:29.02,Thinking,,0,0,0,,then he led his father's old troops\Nand attacked Lújiāng for Yuán Shù.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:46.00,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(225,687.273)\fade(255,0,255,0,450,2000,2380)}Yuán Shù\NStyled: Gōnglù
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.01,0:00:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.47,0:00:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Report! Sūn Cè has returned in triumph from Lújiāng!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:06.90,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1219.091,687.273)\fade(255,0,255,0,390,1900,2260)}Sūn Cè\NStyled: Bófú
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My respects, general!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You've returned victorious! Good! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.69,0:01:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're brave, Bófú!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to our tigerish generals and loyal soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's banquet is to\N welcome Bófú back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Men, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.02,0:01:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring seating!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:01:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bófú.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bófú!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to have a son just like Young Sūn,\NI would die without regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come come come! Everyone! Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Lord values you, Bófú.\NWhy not acknowledge him as your foster father?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He hit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Bófú!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The senior generals Chéng Pǔ \Nand Huáng Gài have come to visit you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They're already at the gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them out! Don't bother me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My father used traverse across the nation.\NWhat a hero he was!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet today, I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you giving me such a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you blame me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, they all mocked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't retaliate.\NInstead, I had to endure insults.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The senior generals refused to leave and waited here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your esteemed father\N had once employed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:40.82,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(184.091,691.364)\fade(255,0,255,0,390,1640,1980)}Chéng Pǔ\NStyled: Démóu
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are unsure of something,\N why not ask us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet here you are, lamenting alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, for your grand strategy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,why not ask Yuán Shù to borrow \Ntroops and go to Jiāngdōng
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of saving your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but in reality to build your own legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Borrow troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But that Yuán Shù is paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he lend the troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we just going to be imprisoned to others' will?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}I have the Heirloom Seal that my father left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}That Yuán Shù has long wanted to obtain such a treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}What if I gave it to him in exchange for troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.10,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1243.636,691.364)\fade(255,0,255,0,330,1550,1900)}Huáng Gài\NStyled: Gōngfù
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Yuán Shù desires the Jade Seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Your father, esteemed general Sūn Jiān,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}from this very Jade Seal had the grudges of all the other lords cast upon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Thus he was shot dead by Liú Biǎo's soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}The life of your father in exchange for the Jade Seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:08:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}How could you gift it to Yuán Shù?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Your concerns are reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}The seal is indeed the treasure of the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}But without troops, we will eventually lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}I want to trade the Jade Seal that took my father's life
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}for a nation he always dreamed of!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Bófú has the courage and \Nshrewdness to do great deeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He will succeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring us wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bófú, if you have something to say, \NI will support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I always think about avenging my late father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and now my old mother and younger siblings\Nare all at Qū'ē, in imminent danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Avenging your father and saving your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the way of a filial child indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, please let me lead a few 1,000 men\N across the Yángzǐ to save my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not be impatient!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When I have spare soldiers, \NI'll naturally let you lead them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, lending soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, right now, I have the\NHeirloom Seal my father once had.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:11:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, if you lend me the troops,\NI would gladly give it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bófú, are you serious about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I will lend you\N3,000 soldiers and 500 horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your status is modest, difficult to hold any power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok! I will appoint you as {\i1}Colonel of Assault{\i0},\N and {\i1}General of Bandit-Fighting{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, you can march to Jiāngdōng. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that person be Zhōu the Youth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:28.95,Default,Zhōu Yú,0,0,0,,Brother Bófú!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! It really is Zhōu the Youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:33.46,Default,Zhōu Yú,0,0,0,,Brother Bófú!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngjǐn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:36.34,Default,Zhōu Yú,0,0,0,,Brother Bófú!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngjǐn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:39.40,Default,Zhōu Yú,0,0,0,,Brother Bófú!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:41.32,Default,Zhōu Yú,0,0,0,,Brother Bófú!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.16,Default,Zhōu Yú,0,0,0,,Brother Bófú!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:05.82,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(210.682,695.455)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,1990,2340)}Zhōu Yú\NStyled: Gōngjǐn
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just going to Dānyáng to visit my uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I would meet you along the way!\NTruly, this is Heaven's will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just as I was leaving Yuán Shù,\NI met you, Gōngjǐn! That would be Heaven's will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard much of your service under Yuán Shù and your skills in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what are your orders now for this expedition?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This expedition was not directed by Yuán Shù,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but the will of my late father's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I will march to Qū'ē, first to conquer\N Liú Yáo, and avenge my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuán Shù has always been \N suspicious of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet this time, he gave his army to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Yuán Shù has not treated you that poorly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Obtaining this army was not without cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed it from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Borrowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuán Shù gave me soldiers and horses
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in exchange for the Heirloom Seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.58,Default,Zhōu Yú,0,0,0,,The Jade Seal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:22.54,Default,Zhōu Yú,0,0,0,,You mean, the one from when the Luòyáng's palace was burning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:26.69,Default,Zhōu Yú,0,0,0,,The seal your father found inside that well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:29.13,Default,Sūn Cè,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.99,Default,Zhōu Yú,0,0,0,,Damn it, that won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:34.49,Default,Sūn Cè,0,0,0,,Won't do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after you've return his troops,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that Yuán Shù won't give up the Jade Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he were to return the Jade Seal,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but I refuse to return his troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! This is no time to jest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For just a mere army,\Nhow can it ever compare to the Heirloom Seal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, you borrowed an army...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,could it be that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, lords fight amongst each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The nation is in anarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That Jade Seal, in the hands of someone like Yuán Shù,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,will only just stoke his delusions of grandeur for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But with an army in my hands, I can expand my domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I will have all the six commanderies\N and eighty counties of Jiāngdōng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will complete my father's great undertaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, your ambitions are grand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come rain or shine, you have my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:16:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngjǐn! With you by my side, \Nmy undertaking is as good as done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You have lofty ambitions, brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but these troops are not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You need the aid of Jiāngdōng's prodigies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, do you know the two Zhāngs of Jiāngdōng?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The two Zhāngs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them is Zhāng Zhāo\Nof Péngchéng, styled Zǐbù,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other is Zhāng Hóng\N from Guǎnglíng, styled Zǐgāng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them possess the talent to rule the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They live here in seclusion to avoid chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not acquire them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! I will personally invite them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:17:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, be cautious when assaulting Qū'ē!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Cautious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the city of Qū'ē, there is a fearsome general.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Tàishǐ Cí.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A fearsome general?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Better than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,His valor is equal to yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If so,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,then I must meet with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you are eager about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Report! Sūn Cè led a force of \Nthirteen cavalrymen to scout on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.94,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1231.364,672.955)\fade(255,0,255,0,460,1460,1860)}Liú Yáo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sūn Cè plans to lure us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not fall for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:18.74,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1098.409,848.864)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,1780,2060)}Tàishǐ Cí\NStyled: Zǐyì
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can lead the vanguard and capture Sūn Cè!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sūn Cè, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Which of you is Sūn Cè?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Tàishǐ Cí of Dōnglái,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,coming to capture Sūn Cè!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So you are Tàishǐ Cí?\NJust who I wanted to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Sūn Cè.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't fear even with the two of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a coward flees!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,General Tàishǐ Cí! Lord Liú Yáo has come to your rescue!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:22:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,General Sūn Cè! Gōngjǐn is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.34,0:23:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, today was dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.01,0:23:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for Zhōu Gōngjǐn's \Ntroops, you would have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tàishǐ Cí really is a true warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tàishǐ Cí dueled sire for\N many bouts, matching every move!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.68,0:23:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly remarkable!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I will capture him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Were it that easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.03,0:23:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, unfold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, keeping this brings ill omen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.28,0:23:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang the robe on the tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.22,0:23:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Brilliant, brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.86,0:23:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngjǐn, what does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:24:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Brother Bófú keeping\N this robe is not without reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.15,0:24:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.42,0:24:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.24,0:24:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait until I subdue Tàishǐ Cí,\Nthen we can explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.80,0:24:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I will lead a cavalry wing to strike Qū'ē. How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.47,0:24:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! It is decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.52,0:24:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sūn Cè's helmet is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.00,0:24:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sūn Cè, come fight me, man against man, if you have the nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.48,0:25:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.01,0:25:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire killed a general by holding him, and another one by shouting!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.45,0:25:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A true Hegemon reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.90,0:25:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Yáo has been defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.56,0:25:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I will capture Tàishǐ Cí!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.86,0:25:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I heard Tàishǐ Cí has recruited \Nable-bodied men from Jīng County!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.86,0:25:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now he has over 2,000 men!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.00,0:26:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He claims vengeance for Liú Yáo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.80,0:26:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All he has recruited in his haste are savages.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.40,0:26:10.14,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1186.364,695.455)\fade(255,0,255,0,350,1240,1720)}Zhāng Zhāo\NStyled: Zǐbù
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.73,0:26:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Unseasoned and vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.23,0:26:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to capture Tàishǐ Cí!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.50,0:26:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, what are your suggestions?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.10,0:26:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.95,0:26:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We can divide our army into three routes,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.05,0:26:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,From West, North, and South,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.80,0:26:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack Jīng County from three sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.38,0:26:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave only the East gate for passage
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.25,0:26:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,then lay an ambush about \Ntwenty-five lǐ from the East gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.56,0:26:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tàishǐ Cí will be there, exhausted, and ripe for capture!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.43,0:26:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A good plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.97,0:26:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhōu Tài!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.27,0:26:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.54,0:26:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Scale the city walls at night, and start a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.38,0:27:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tàishǐ Cí will run!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.30,0:27:01.68,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1257.955,695.455)\fade(255,0,255,0,410,1345,1345)}Zhōu Tài\NStyled: Yòupíng
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.91,0:27:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.00,0:27:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huáng Gài.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.75,0:27:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.22,0:27:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Have your squad to set up\N ambushes at all vital crossings,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.55,0:27:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dig out pitfalls or set a horse-tripper.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.69,0:27:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to catch Tàishǐ Cí alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.66,0:27:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.25,0:28:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Zhōu Tài has succeeded!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.84,0:28:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Capture Tàishǐ Cí, alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.24,0:28:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Breach the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.97,0:29:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tàishǐ Cí! Where are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.94,0:29:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Capture Tàishǐ Cí!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.83,0:30:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why treat the general like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.30,0:30:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Untie him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.52,0:31:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies for the discourtesy, general.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.75,0:31:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.04,0:31:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've longed to have your cooperation\N like good rain after a drought.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.91,0:31:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're a true fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.15,0:31:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Yáo is a pismire, unable to use your skills, thus he was defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.00,0:31:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been suffocating for you, great general.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.13,0:31:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If my subordinates have offended you,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.30,0:31:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I would ask for you to forgive me as their superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.30,0:31:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a defeated soldier, why waste time?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.01,0:31:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I crave Jiāngnán, so I long wanted to meet a foe such as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.28,0:31:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hardly rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.92,0:32:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I only regret that I didn't meet you sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.36,0:32:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I can't ever perform great deeds with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.54,0:32:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A great pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.84,0:32:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Zǐyì, why are you still standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.77,0:32:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just please come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.49,0:32:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Zǐyì, we are at war with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.23,0:32:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to capture me, would you harm me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.57,0:33:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't... know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.88,0:33:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. How frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.25,0:33:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If we fought each other, if I were\N to receive no reinforcements,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.68,0:33:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,if you and I went on like this, \Nwould you know who wins?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.86,0:33:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't... know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.30,0:33:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.85,0:33:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Zǐyì, ever since I led my first army,\NI have not met a rival such as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.14,0:33:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Zǐyì, you are a true hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.77,0:33:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This robe is a proof of that, Zǐyì!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.45,0:33:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the robe hung to remind me that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.28,0:33:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,there are people beyond a person,\Nand skies beyond a sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.72,0:33:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wandered for so long, and have never met a worthy lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.06,0:33:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,General, if you don't mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.43,0:33:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I will serve you and dedicate my all to your cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.03,0:34:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With you by my side, \Nwe can accomplish great things!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.67,0:34:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! Prepare a banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.84,0:34:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring wine for Zǐyì!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.95,0:34:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.80,0:34:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liú suffered a massive defeat \Nand their morale is low.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.84,0:34:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go back, rally the remnants,\N then lead them to assist you!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.09,0:34:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.56,0:34:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, General, for your loyal heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.57,0:34:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. I will return with my men, tomorrow at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.28,0:34:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.02,0:34:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Zǐyì takes his leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.05,0:34:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.15,0:35:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way! \NLet Zǐyì through!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.23,0:35:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.24,0:35:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, of old, when Shāng Yāng was enacting his reforms,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.58,0:35:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,he put a log as a symbol of trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.22,0:35:58.04,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Shāng Yāng was a Legalist scholar during the Warring States era \Nwho reformed and strengthened the state of Qin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.58,0:35:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We are following his example,\N and put up this pole as a symbol of trust too
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.78,0:35:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to indicate if it's noon,\Nand see if Tàishǐ Cí would come!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.99,0:36:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}To build a legacy, you must first employ the able.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.55,0:36:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}To employ the able, you must never suspect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.08,0:36:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}To hold such suspicions, \Nhow would their trust be won?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.50,0:36:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}When my father left, \Nhe left behind two items.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.85,0:36:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}One was the Heirloom Seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.05,0:36:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}I have traded it for an army.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.05,0:36:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}And the other? It is this sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.25,0:36:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Today, this sword shall be my pledge!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.52,0:36:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}I, Sūn Cè, employ people, not suspect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.85,0:36:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}I believe Zǐyì is a man of his words!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.55,0:36:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}By noon, Zǐyì will return!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.33,0:37:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord! It's almost noon already, \Nand Tàishǐ Cí hasn't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.84,0:37:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You  shouldn't have let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.45,0:37:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have trusted that knave!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.81,0:37:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It is already noon, yet there is no sight of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.38,0:37:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He fled!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.65,0:37:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.16,0:37:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's noon!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.10,0:37:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Generals, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.50,0:37:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We agreed to meet at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.23,0:37:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not past noon yet.\NHow could you say that Zǐyì will be late?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.51,0:38:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, let's go and check!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.70,0:39:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I late?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.00,0:39:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly at noon!\NYou truly are a just and honorable warrior, Ziyì!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.55,0:39:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.86,0:39:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngjǐn!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.00,0:39:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After the battle of Shéntíng Ridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.37,0:39:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I hung your torn robe in the tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.74,0:39:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was confused, \Nbut only Gōngjǐn understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.71,0:39:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, you can explain it to everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.00,0:39:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}When heroes meet in battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.17,0:39:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}they are elated for the spoils!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.55,0:39:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Bófú took the robe from the battle,
